android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

manifest_analysis.title:
Service (androidx.work.impl.background.systemjob.SystemJobService) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.BIND_JOB_SERVICE
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

playstore_details.title: Coinpay: Buy & Send Bitcoin Fast Cryptocurrency 😇
playstore_details.description:
Coinpay is a Social Bitcoin Wallet for Bitcoin and popular cryptocurrencies. Coinpay lets bitcoiners buy, send, and interact with the Bitcoin Blockchain in seconds rather than minutes unlike other crypto exchanges. Coinpay is fast too. It takes seconds to set up an anonymous wallet and account. 

Coinpay is trusted in over 100 countries worldwide, and the Coinpay team believes that Bitcoin will change the world as a currency. We encourage our users to use Bitcoin as an investment and a currency to use in the trade of goods and services. Coinpay allows users to get started with cryptocurrency in seconds rather than days or hours - unlike Coinbase and Binance. We require no personal information when signing up, so users can remain anonymous. We are a non-custodial wallet, so users can send Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies globally with direct access to the blockchain. 

With Coinpay you can easily purchase (with debit card, credit card, and Apple Pay), send, and receive Bitcoin, Litecoin, and Ethereum. We provide usernames associated with your accounts public keys to make sending bitcoin and crypto to friends and family fast, easy, and secure. 

The cryptocurrency in your wallets is always yours because your private key is only stored on your phone's hardware. Coinpay stores your funds in a decentralized manner because we do not have access to any of our users funds, and you always have access to your cryptocurrencies private keys. 

Wallet Storage

• Create a new Bitcoin wallet or import your existing one using your private key

• View your public and private keys, even when you're offline

• Use your public key to import funds from exchanges, or have external users send or pay you cryptocurrency or Bitcoin 

• Easily sign and send transactions on the blockchain 

• View your previous transactions in one place

• Backup your wallets by exporting your private keys. We allow users to print out a paper key for cold storage in a safe / hidden location. 

Easy Transactions

• Quickly send from your Bitcoin Wallet by clicking a user and entering an amount

• Receive notifications when friends or family pay or send crypto to you

• Enter a dollar amount when sending Bitcoin, Ethereum, or Litecoin

• Add a memo to your blockchain transactions for accounting purposes

Social Interface

• Coinpay users can pay you by simply clicking on your username in the search bar

• Add friends and family to send them cryptocurrency instead of asking 
for their public key - this makes sending Bitcoin take seconds rather than minutes 

• Customize your profile so others can easily find you

• There is even an option to share your transaction on the social newsfeed if you want to. There is also the option to remain anonymous too. 

Coinpay makes sending and buying Bitcoin easy and secure. We allow our users to remain anonymous and set up a bitcoin wallet that can directly interact with the Bitcoin blockchain. Whether it’s for an investment or for free trade download Coinpay and buy, send, and sell with Bitcoin today!
